2 COVID-19 visualizations

library(tidyverse)
library(COVID19)
# Exam situations in USA
covid_us <- covid19("USA", level = 2, verbose = FALSE)
# head(covid_us)
ggplot(covid_us, aes(x = date, y = confirmed)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  facet_wrap(~id)

covid_us %>% 
  dplyr::filter(id %in% unique(covid_us$id)[1:5]) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = date, y = confirmed)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  facet_wrap(~id)
## Warning: Removed 13 row(s) containing missing values (geom_path).
